## 5. Backend Dockerfile

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.9

WORKDIR /app

COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install -r requirements.txt

COPY . .

CMD ["uvicorn", "main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8000"]
```

### Explanation

* Uses Python base image
* Installs dependencies
* Copies source code
* Runs FastAPI server

